taking guitar lessons to a new level this is a great dvd . the guitar style spectrum is covered here with country , blues , and rock , with tips and tricks to enhance your own style . greg uses fender strats and telecasters ( my favorite guitars ) throughout the video and explains and demonstrates his unique style in a way that you can pick up on with a little practice and not be totally discouraged . this dvd is filled with humor , great teaching and superb pointers for expanding your technique . if you are a fan of greg koch or would want to make your playing really stand out , you need this video